Package: twigg
Title: Tool for screening item response data 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Sebastian", "Kvist", , "zkb139alumni.ku.dk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: functions to help screen IRT data and determine if a Rasch model 
    is applicable. The implementaion is based on the screening process proposed 
    by Karl Bang Christensen and Svend Kreiner. The package includes an 
    artificial example dataset adapted from the eRm package.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
